.SH ks\-mp3 \- Convert video/audio file to MP3 (Audio) Format.
.SS Syntax:
.IP
.EX
$ ks\-mp3 </absolute/path/song.ogg> </path/prefix_name>
.EE
.SS Default configuration:
.IP \[bu] 2
